MID_支援_サイゾウ_ベルカ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$WaI know you. You're Nohr's assassin.\nBelka, right?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa...$k$pSaizou, ninja of Hoshido.\nWhat do you want?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|Hm...? So, you've heard of me.\nJust as I have heard of you.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes. The name Saizou of Hoshido is known\nfar and wide across the Kingdom of Nohr.$k$p$E怒,|He is the right hand of the crown prince.\nAn assassin of great skill.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaAnd you... from a young age you've\nkilled without hesitation. $k$pI have heard the rumors, the stories\ntold of a child...$k$pThe ruthless, murdering hand of a child.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|...I see.$k$p$E通常,|How many... have you killed?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|...Why?\nDo you keep count?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|When I was an assassin, I did.$k$pBut after Lady Camilla took me in...\nI stopped.$k$p$Eキメ,|I don't know if it's\ngood or bad...$k$pBut it was the only thing that changed.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|Is that so?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|I gave my answer.\nYour turn.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|I... can't forget.$k$pEven if I try not to think about it...$k$pEven if I try to forget... They're like\nscars on my heart, $k$p The faces and names of the people\nI've killed are engraved into me.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|...I see.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|That I should join hands with an assassin\nwho serves the kingdom of my enemy... $k$pIt can only be fate.$k$pWe hold some things in common.\nLords that we must protect.$k$pSo, Belka.\nI'll rely on you.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaUnderstood.$k
MID_支援_サイゾウ_ベルカ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$WaSo, Belka. $k$pDuring your time as an assassin, did you\never take on targets alone?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|Always.\nI didn't need any help.$k$pHowever... After Lady Camilla took me in...\nIt wasn't the same.$k$pWith special forces at my command,\nI slay multitudes at a time.$k$p$E通常,|...What about you?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaThe circumstances surrounding many of my\nmissions required I go undercover alone.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I see...\nIt must be quite taxing to be a spy.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|Yes. There was one mission in particular.\nIt happened a few years ago...$k$pI killed a Nohrian Duke.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|My mission was to assassinate a noble\nin the Eastern quarter of Nohr's capital.$k$p$E怒,|It was painstaking work, but in the end,\nhe was completely deceived.$k$pAfter I took him out, my target changed\nto the rest of the noble family. $k$pI saw... their faces plastered\nwith betrayal... and with loathing...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|...?\nWhat's wrong, Belka?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Their family name was... Boldt.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|How did you know that?!$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|...I see.\nThe one who killed him... It was you.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|What do you mean?\nDid you know him?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|No... there's no point in it now.\nForget I said anything.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wd$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|H-Hey... Wait!\nBelka!!$k$p…………$k$p$E苦,汗|What was that all about...?$k
MID_支援_サイゾウ_ベルカ_Ａ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$WaBelka,\nI'd like to talk about―$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I told you to forget about it.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|I can't forget. It makes me sick to think...\nI-I got ahold of some intel on the incident.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|...!!$k$p$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|You were there. The Boldt family had you\nunder hire.$k$pAnd you cut down Lord Suruga\nfrom Hoshido...$k$pThe man who hired me to\nkill the Boldt family.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|………$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|Because of that, when the Suruga family\narranged for my return to Nohr...$k$pThat was when I...$k$pI... did what I did to the Boldt family...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,|That's enough... Stop.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|The reason you close your ears...$k$pIs it because you don't want to know\nhow meaningless your actions were?$k$pYou prefer to live in ignorance?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|I'm no different. It's honestly...\nIt's all... unbearable.$k$pAll this, a vicious cycle.$k$pRevenge makes a chain. It links murder\nupon murder down to the depths of hell...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes...\nThat's the truth.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|To make an end of it...\nThat's why we go to war, isn't it?$k$pWe wash away the blood of our sins\nwith more blood...$k$pWe must end this way of thinking.$k$pYou think so too, don't you?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes.\nFor that very reason we joined forces.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E笑,|Exactly. I want to make haste and break\nthis cycle! To bring peace to the earth!$k$pIn order to manage that,\nI need your strength.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Understood.\nI'll give it my all.$k
MID_支援_サイゾウ_ベルカ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$WaBelka, got a moment?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaWhat is it?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaBear with me. $k$pNot long ago, we took a pledge\ntogether to bring peace to the earth.$k$p$E怒,|I propose we take\nanother pledge.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|Another?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaYes. After all, we two bear the same burden.\nWe spent our life with unclean hands.$k$pEven if we bring peace\nto the world...$k$pWe have a gaping\nhole in ourselves.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|True...$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaEven so...\nWe seek peace.$k$pAm I wrong?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Peace...$k$p...What do you mean?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaLet's live together, Belka.$k$pI want to live beside you, to build a\nhome where only you and I know rest.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,照|S-Saizou...!$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,照|Even if the world holds us in contempt\nbecause of our past...$k$pEven if every last man\nturns their back on us...$k$pI... I will never betray you.\nI swear to stay beside you, always.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa…………$k$p$E通常,照|So... there is still some\nemotion left in me, after all.$k$pI... want to find peace...$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E笑,照|I'm sure we can manage it,\nif we're together.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes.\nI'll... stand beside you.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,照|It no longer matters who despises us.\nWe have each other.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑2,照|...Yes.$k
